  <li>Fixed a bug that caused Disqus to load the same thread on all pages (<a href="https://github.com/qwtel/hydejack/pull/52">#53</a>)</li>
  <li>Fixed a bug that prevented Disqus comments to be loaded on sites that didn‚Äôt cause scroll events</li>
  <li>Fixed a bug that caused Disqus to be loaded over HTTP instead of HTTPS.</li>
  <li>Fixed a bug that caused an extra space in URLs (<a href="https://github.com/qwtel/hydejack/pull/55">#55</a>).</li>
  <li>Comments no longer show up in the print version of the page.</li>
</ul>

