  <li>Fixed a bug that caused the drawer flicker/open unexpectedly when scrolling in mobile browsers.</li>
  <li>Fixed how <code class="highlighter-rouge">image</code> works when using the <code class="highlighter-rouge">jekyll-seo-tag</code> plugin.</li>
